    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for this reliable beauty! It\u2019s been a fantastic ride for me and is still in really solid shape. It has a few minor signs of love here and there\u2014just the usual stuff from some great road trips\u2014but it runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. I've made sure to keep up with it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 31500.0,
