    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its individual throttle bodies to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically robust, the VANOS system has been overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014critical preventative measures for this chassis. It retains its factory limited-slip differential and M-tuned suspension geometry, offering exceptional turn-in and corner-exit traction. While the aesthetic shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. Recent fluid analysis confirms the health of the rod bearings. A true enthusiast's spec ready for the canyons.",
